{
  "texts": [
    "Data were collected from July to August 2024.",
    "CTSA leaders who responded to the initial invitation received a follow-up email with the survey link.",
    "A PDF version of the survey was provided to help participants prepare by reviewing questions offline before completing the survey online.",
    "Participants could return to the survey if necessary.",
    "Quantitative data from the survey were analyzed using various methods."
  ]
}